file.name: clashing-path-merged.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: "Merged documentation"
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  "/foo/foo":
    summary: "foo endpoint"
    get:
      summary: "get foos"
      operationId: "getAllFoo"
      responses:
        200:
          description: "success"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/foo"
    post:
      summary: "create a new foo"
      operationId: "createFoo"
      responses:
        200:
          description: success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/foo"
          links:
            "list":
              operationId: getAllFoo
  "/foo/login":
    post:
      summary: "user log in"
      responses:
        200:
          description: "success"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  sessionKey:
                    type: string
        400:
          description: "failure"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/error"
  "/bar/bar":
    summary: "bar endpoint"
    get:
      summary: "get bar"
      operationId: "getAllBar"
      responses:
        200:
          description: "success"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: "#/components/schemas/bar"
    post:
      summary: "create a new bar"
      operationId: "createBar"
      responses:
        200:
          description: success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/bar"
          links:
            "list":
              operationId: getAllBar
  "/bar/login":
    post:
      summary: "user log in"
      responses:
        202:
          description: "success"
        400:
          description: "failure"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/error"
components:
  schemas:
    foo:
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
      required: 
        - id
        - name
    error:
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
      required:
        - code
        - message
    bar:
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
      required: 
        - id
        - name
